title: BBC Keith Richards The Origin of the Species Directors Cut 1080p
description:
Keith Richards: The Origin of the Species Director's Cut

Biography Documentary hosted by Julien Temple, published by BBC in 2016 - English narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/5/5e/Keith-Richards-The-Origin-of-the-Species-Director-s-Cut-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
A Julien Temple documentary essay film about Keith Richards's postwar childhood and adolescence in Dartford and London. Exploring the cultural undercurrents and transformative thinking which occurred in England between 1945 and 1962 and made possible the worldwide explosion of British rock music during the 60s, in which Keith played such a crucial role.
